  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为物流追踪系统画一个完整的架构流程图。核心是从用户查询运单号开始，经过DNS、CDN，最后落到存储层。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "DNS",
        "CDN",
        "STORAGE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。用户节点我打算叫Logistics_TrackingNumber，代表查询入口。DNS层用Logistics_StockLevel来命名，里面放Route 53。这样层级关系对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "DNS",
        "R53"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，DNS层确实和库存水位监控相关，用StockLevel命名合理。CDN层我想用FleetManagement和Warehouse来区分边缘计算和函数处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CDN",
        "EDGE",
        "LAMBDA"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，CDN子图里我放了EDGE节点叫Logistics_FleetManagement，LAMBDA节点叫Logistics_Warehouse。还需要证书和缓存节点吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CDN",
        "EDGE",
        "LAMBDA",
        "CERT",
        "CACHE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要，CERT和CACHE都用TrackingNumber命名，因为证书和缓存策略都是围绕运单查询设计的。存储层OAI用Warehouse，FILES用FleetManagement。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CERT",
        "CACHE",
        "OAI",
        "FILES"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加。现在连接关系怎么定？从USER到R53应该是HTTPS协议吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "R53"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，USER到R53标注HTTPS。然后R53指向EDGE，EDGE到LAMBDA，LAMBDA到CERT，CERT再到CACHE，形成CDN内部的处理链。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "R53",
        "EDGE",
        "LAMBDA",
        "CERT",
        "CACHE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "CDN内部链路画好了。CACHE到存储层的OAI需要特殊标注吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CACHE",
        "OAI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要，CACHE到OAI这条线要标注'OAI Only'，强调只有OAI能直接访问存储，这是安全策略。然后OAI再到FILES。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CACHE",
        "OAI",
        "FILES"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "标注已添加。现在给各层加颜色区分吧？USER用蓝色系，DNS用黄色，CDN用粉色，STORAGE用绿色？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "DNS",
        "CDN",
        "STORAGE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，具体色值你定，但要保证对比度。USER用浅蓝底深蓝边，DNS浅黄底深黄边。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "DNS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "颜色已应用。CDN和STORAGE的颜色我也按你说的方案设置了。整体结构看起来没问题了，你检查一下？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CDN",
        "STORAGE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我发现CDN子图的名称有问题。你写的是CDN，但按我们的命名规范，子图名称应该和里面某个节点一致。你看STORAGE子图名称是Logistics_TrackingNumber，但CDN子图名称只是CDN，不一致。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，统一命名规范。那CDN子图名称也改成Logistics_TrackingNumber？还是和里面某个具体节点对齐？",
      "elements_involved": [
